rows.label: tlk47100072_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I can sense the destinies of individual
people, but not Acedia as a whole.

rows.label: tlk47100072_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I wonder what part Acedia has to play
in the great tapestry of life?

rows.label: tlk47100072_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Phonexes love hearing stories, so I'm
very curious to learn Acedia's story!

rows.label: tlk47100072_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I can picture it now...a fur-tingling tale
of a destiny unlike no other! Ooh, I'm
itching to hear it already!
